{"data":{"id":"https://worldcouncilforhealth.substack.com/p/whats-up-with-professor-bhakdis-legal","title":"What's Up With Professor Bhakdiâ€™s Legal Case?","link":"https://worldcouncilforhealth.substack.com/p/whats-up-with-professor-bhakdis-legal","pubDate":"Fri, 21 Feb 2025 11:14:25 GMT","description":"With this latest postponement, the punishment by process being inflicted on this upstanding scientist is a sad reflection of the state of justice in Germany.","content":"<div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef168de-dca4-4f64-bac4-043ff352096d_900x473.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef168de-dca4-4f64-bac4-043ff352096d_900x473.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef168de-dca4-4f64-bac4-043ff352096d_900x473.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef168de-dca4-4f64-bac4-043ff352096d_900x473.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef168de-dca4-4f64-bac4-043ff352096d_900x473.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef168de-dca4-4f64-bac4-043ff352096d_900x473.jpeg\" width=\"900\" height=\"473\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6ef168de-dca4-4f64-bac4-043ff352096d_900x473.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:473,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:49881,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef168de-dca4-4f64-bac4-043ff352096d_900x473.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef168de-dca4-4f64-bac4-043ff352096d_900x473.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef168de-dca4-4f64-bac4-043ff352096d_900x473.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef168de-dca4-4f64-bac4-043ff352096d_900x473.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></div></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Prof. Sucharit Bhakdi, a renowned microbiologist and former chair of the Doctors for Covid Ethics and co-founder of the <a href=\"https://www.mwgfd.org/\">MWGFD</a> has been embroiled in a legal battle in Germany since 2021. The case stems from two public statements he made in April and September 2021, which led to charges of <em>Volksverhetzung</em> (incitement of hatred) and an alleged trivialization of the Holocaust.</p><p>The first charge relates to an April 2021 interview where Bhakdi criticized Israel&#8217;s Covid-19 policies, drawing parallels to historical events. The second charge arises from a September 2021 speech in Kiel, where he likened the global vaccination campaign to a \"second Holocaust.\" These statements sparked widespread backlash, leading to multiple criminal complaints filed by individuals and organisations, including the Jewish Community Berlin.</p><p>Prof. Bhakdi has since repeatedly expressed his high views on Jewish culture and people and that the allegations were put entirely out of context.</p><h4><strong>Key legal developments</strong></h4><ol><li><p><strong>Initial charges and freispruch (acquittal):</strong></p><ul><li><p>In May 2023, after a one-day trial at the Amtsgericht Pl&#246;n (Pl&#246;n District Court), Judge Malte Grundmann acquitted Bhakdi of both charges. The court found that his statements, while controversial, did not meet the legal threshold for criminal liability under German law.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Prosecution&#8217;s appeal:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Dissatisfied with the verdict, the Schleswig-Holstein General Prosecutor&#8217;s Office, led by Chief Prosecutor Silke F&#252;ssinger, filed an appeal. The prosecution argued that Bhakdi&#8217;s statements trivialized the Holocaust and incited hatred, warranting a reevaluation of the case.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Latest update:</strong></p><ul><li><p>The appeal hearing, originally scheduled for <strong>February 27-28, 2025</strong>, at the Landgericht Kiel (Kiel Regional Court), has been <strong>postponed</strong>. New dates are yet to be announced. This delay follows the prosecution&#8217;s decision to continue pursuing the case despite the initial acquittal.</p></li></ul><div><hr></div></li></ol><div class=\"digest-post-embed\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;1428e532-560a-4771-b739-21935a15405d&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Sucharit Bhakdi, Emeritus Professor of the Johannes Gutenberg University in Mainz, a specialist in microbiology and infectious disease epidemiology, and the founder and chairman of a society of physicians and scientists for health, freedom and democracy, was introduced by Christof Plothe, DO, who described him as one of his &#8220;personal heroes&#8221; and &#8220;a shin&#8230;&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;md&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Prof Sucharit Bhakdi: The Eternal Dangers of RNA Vaccines &#8212; A Horror Story&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:106680170,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;World Council for Health&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;The World Council for Health is a non-profit initiative for the people, that is informed and funded by the people. \\n\\nThere is a better way and we are committed to creating it together with you!&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/16ad6c42-2750-4030-aef4-de60880a9156_1200x630.jpeg&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:100}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2023-11-03T12:11:28.520Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substack-video.s3.amazonaws.com/video_upload/post/138527748/45f381ef-572f-4859-ad4d-86e309908cdd/transcoded-00001.png&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://worldcouncilforhealth.substack.com/p/bhakdi-plasmidgate&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:138527748,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;video&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:79,&quot;comment_count&quot;:19,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;World Council for Health&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd555faff-937e-4eef-997f-3c14a25a763c_345x345.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}\"></div><div><hr></div><h4><strong>Free speech is under attack </strong></h4><p>The case has drawn significant attention as it represents an attack on free speech, particularly regarding dissenting views on Covid-19 policies.</p><p>Procedural complexities, including disputes over evidence and allegations of judicial bias have marked the legal proceedings. Bhakdi&#8217;s defence team has consistently argued that his statements were taken out of context and that the charges are politically motivated.</p><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://worldcouncilforhealth.substack.com/p/whats-up-with-professor-bhakdis-legal?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://worldcouncilforhealth.substack.com/p/whats-up-with-professor-bhakdis-legal?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share\"><span>Share</span></a></p><h4><strong>What happens next? </strong></h4><p>As the case moves to the Landgericht Kiel, the outcome of the appeal will be closely watched. For now, the postponement of the hearing means that the legal saga continues, with no immediate resolution in sight. We&#8217;ll continue to keep you updated as new developments arise. </p><p>The World Council for Health firmly stands behind a very competent, humble and compassionate hero of our time: Prof Sucharit Bhakdi, and hopes that the case against him will be dropped soon to enable a true scientific debate on the events of the last years and their consequences.</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8540ef62-2e56-4ccd-93f9-dfb47325b30c_688x275.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8540ef62-2e56-4ccd-93f9-dfb47325b30c_688x275.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8540ef62-2e56-4ccd-93f9-dfb47325b30c_688x275.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8540ef62-2e56-4ccd-93f9-dfb47325b30c_688x275.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com